<L><PB N="118" REF="029659_0130_0FE21428CB66F200">The Trojan &s;tole the bough of gold,</L>
<L>And, le&s;t grim Cerb'rus &s;hould make head,</L>
<L>Stuff'd both his fobs with <NOTE N="*" PLACE="foot">&mdash; Medicatam frugibus offam. Aeneid, lib. vi. 410</NOTE> gingerbread;</L>
<L>Behold at Britain's utmo&s;t &s;hifts,</L>
