<L>The Chief emerging from his <NOTE PLACE="foot">"&dagger; Alluding to <GAP DESC="illegible" REASON="indecipherable" EXTENT="1 word"> well-known fact of Cornwallis's taking up his re&s;idence in a cave, during the &s;iege of York-Town."</NOTE> cave,</L>
